# Testing

- Framework: `rove`. Each test file uses `(:use :cl :rove)`.
- Test systems use explicit `:components` in `.asd` (NOT `package-inferred-system`).
- Import class symbols if passing them to `from-json` or similar symbol-dispatched functions.
- Run tests: `qlot exec ros -e '(asdf:test-system "cl-oci")'`
- Integration tests assume a local OCI registry at `http://localhost:5050`.
- Use `(sb-ext:disable-debugger)` when running tests non-interactively.
